originalText.text: Dr. Jeffrey Naiditch is an especially effective and compassionate doctor.  His approach to the health of his client is by way of unhurried conversation.  My experience with his personable approach is that influences on my health or health problem can be found in places in my life where I wasn't looking.  There is a feeling that you are in the hands of community's family doctor.

originalText.text:
It took me 20 years to find a doctor who not only listened to what my problems were he actually helped solve my medical issues and assisted me with finding the right specialists who would solve my medical issues. He also worked with me to help me navigate the complex healthcare  bureaucracy of prior approvals, special aurthorizations etc. This is a small intimate practice focused on the patient. His assistant is terrific. It is refreshing to walk into a doctors office, they know your name, the staff is pleasant and helpful....rather than walk into a doctors office with four nurses and three assistants, they don't know your name, and you wait twenty minutes,  to see the doctor for a total of ten minutes.

It is refreshing to walk into a doctors office
